<font color="#FF0000">MOVING FORWARD</font><br>
<tt>Sun Nov  2 22:54:10 US/Eastern 1997
</tt><p>
When we are born we start down the road of life.  Our decisions and the events in our life influence the different paths we take.  The character of the man ensures that he does not get lost in the maze of possibilities and stays on the true road.  We find that there are many ways to get to our destination and equally as many ways to be lost forever.<br><br>
Vietnam was merely one of those decisions or inevitable events on the road to where I am today.  I am sure that I gained from that experience and do not question why.<br><br>
An event in the past can no longer be questioned.  The only task is to go forward and not wander aimlessly in the events of history.  We as BOC will ensure that there is someone to take the hand of those who need to find their way.<br><br>
I am lucky to have come this far.  My only wish is to continue to the final goal and leave a legacy to quide my children<br><br>
YBOC<br>

<p><code>--   (SW) </code><p>


